channel.title: Help with error
channel.description:
Ok so i have been for the past 3 days trying to find out how to fix the "error_game_js5connect" Error. So far i have been unsuccessful :(. Anyhow so i am posting how do i fix it. People have told me some reasons it is doing it are:
1.) Wrong IP address. 2.) Server is not online/Rune source first. 3.) Environmental Variables are not set
and i have made a host on no-ip.com and put that host name in the client.java file where it said "127.0.0.1" and i compiled, ran and it still didnt work. I dont know how to see if the server is online (i am new at this stuff) so idk what im doing there and i always make sure i run the Source first. I watched a vid on how to set EV so im pretty sure there good. BTW i have a 317 that is working just fine atm but this 562 keeps saying "error_game_js5connect". The Client and stuff im using for the 562 is from "Element-X". So does anyone have any suggestions whatsoever?!!? (Also if needed i can teamview and i have msn) THANKS, T A N K :cool:
